Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Elbow MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mass/Osteolysis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and preselected
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Localization/Extension' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Humerus, lateral epicondyle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Humerus, medial epicondyle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Humerus, distal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Radius, proximal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ulna, proximal' checkbox is enabled

And 'Epiphyseal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Metaphyseal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Diaphyseal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled

When I select 'I know' radio button
Then 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Histologically confirmed' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Histologically confirmed' checkbox
Then 'Benign' radio button is enabled
And 'Malignant' radio button is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
